---
import PageHeader from "../components/PageHeader.astro";
import { AppConfig } from "../config/AppConfig";
import Main from "../layouts/Main.astro";
---

<Main
  meta={{
    title: `About me | ${AppConfig.title}`,
    description: AppConfig.description,
    image: "/assets/og-images/about.png",
  }}
>
  <div class="pb-8 pt-2">
    <PageHeader 
      title="About Me" 
      emoji="💡" 
      description="Builder, tinkerer, and lifelong learner."
    />
  </div>

  <div class="space-y-12">
    <!-- Section 01: The Journey -->
    <section id="journey" class="space-y-4">
      <span class="font-mono text-xxs uppercase tracking-widest text-zinc-400 block mb-2">[01] The Journey</span>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
        <p>
          I&apos;m a technology entrepreneur from India 🇮🇳 with over a decade of experience in the software industry. 
          My journey began with a deep fascination for the web, which eventually led me to co-found 
          <a href="https://skcript.com" target="_blank" class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-200 underline decoration-zinc-300 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-zinc-900 dark:decoration-zinc-700 dark:hover:decoration-zinc-200 transition-colors">Skcript</a>, 
          a technology consulting company that has been solving complex engineering problems for ten years.
        </p>
        <p>
          Over the years, I've built countless projects, primarily within the JavaScript and TypeScript ecosystems. 
          What started as writing code has evolved into a passion for building sustainable products and helping 
          other product owners bring their visions to life.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 02: Current Focus -->
    <section id="focus" class="space-y-4">
      <span class="font-mono text-xxs uppercase tracking-widest text-zinc-400 block mb-2">[02] Current Focus</span>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <a href="https://featureos.app?utm_source=varunraj_in" target="_blank" class="plain group block p-4 rounded-lg border border-zinc-900 hover:border-zinc-700 transition-all bg-zinc-900/50 !no-underline">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-zinc-100 group-hover:underline decoration-1 underline-offset-4">FeatureOS</h3>
            <span class="font-mono text-xxs text-emerald-400 bg-emerald-900/30 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">Active</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
            The premier platform for product teams to collect feedback, manage roadmaps, and publish changelogs.
          </p>
        </a>

        <a href="https://supportwire.io?utm_source=varunraj_in" target="_blank" class="plain group block p-4 rounded-lg border border-zinc-900 hover:border-zinc-700 transition-all bg-zinc-900/50 !no-underline">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-zinc-100 group-hover:underline decoration-1 underline-offset-4">SupportWire</h3>
            <span class="font-mono text-xxs text-sky-400 bg-sky-900/30 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">In Progress</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
             A high-performance live chat and customer support platform engineered for modern startups as a fast and intuitive alternative to enterprise solutions.
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 03: Beyond Code -->
    <section id="interests" class="space-y-4">
      <span class="font-mono text-xxs uppercase tracking-widest text-zinc-400 block mb-2">[03] Beyond Code</span>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
        <p>
          When I'm away from the keyboard, I'm usually exploring the physical world. I have a deep appreciation for 
          nature and adventure travel—collecting memories and souvenirs from every new place I visit.
        </p>
        <p>
          Recently, my curiosity has expanded into hardware. I spend my weekends building AI agents, 
          maintaining a self-hosted homelab, and designing functional prints for my 3D printer. 
          It's a chaotic but rewarding mix of soldering irons, PLA filament, and Python scripts.
        </p>
        <p>
          I also have a strong affinity for 
          <a href="/blog/why-we-should-care-about-good-design" class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-200 underline decoration-zinc-300 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-zinc-900 dark:decoration-zinc-700 dark:hover:decoration-zinc-200 transition-colors">good design</a>, 
          whether it's in software, architecture, or everyday objects.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Main>
